<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>彭博加密货币</title><link>https://bloomberg.com/crypto/</link><description>彭博加密货币</description><lastBuildDate>Thu, 26 Feb 2026 12:33:30 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>与特朗普家族有关的比特币矿工受到加密货币崩溃的打击</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-02-26/bitcoin-miner-tied-to-trump-family-pummeled-by-crypto-crash</link><description>美国比特币公司（American Bitcoin Corp.）是特朗普家族支持的矿商，乘着加密货币的热潮在纳斯达克首次亮相时表现出色，但现在却陷入了该行业自 2022 年以来最严重的溃败之中。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/i4BHJ71PRv94/v1/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 26 Feb 2026 11:49:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-02-26/bitcoin-miner-tied-to-trump-family-pummeled-by-crypto-crash</guid></item><item><title>Bailey 向 FSB 提出新的投标以启动跨境支付工作</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-02-26/bailey-makes-new-fsb-bid-to-kickstart-cross-border-payments-work</link><description>在官员们承认各国“不太可能”实现 2027 年设定的目标后，英格兰银行行长安德鲁·贝利 (Andrew Bailey) 发起了一项新举措，以平滑传统资金的跨境流动。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/i9T8onQ.AcqM/v0/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 26 Feb 2026 08:45:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-02-26/bailey-makes-new-fsb-bid-to-kickstart-cross-border-payments-work</guid></item><item><title>1万亿美元的残骸中隐藏着比特币的牛市理由</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-02-25/the-bull-case-for-bitcoin-is-hiding-in-the-1-trillion-wreckage</link><description>比特币自 10 月份高点以来已下跌近一半。几乎从所有方面来看，此次抛售都是自 FTX 崩溃以来最严重的一次。但残骸的中心有一个谜团：在繁荣时期围绕代币建立的制度脚手架并没有随之倒塌。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/ikpnPZCCHL.I/v3/1200x-1.png" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 25 Feb 2026 18:44:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-02-25/the-bull-case-for-bitcoin-is-hiding-in-the-1-trillion-wreckage</guid></item><item><title>随着风险偏好回归加密货币，比特币逼近 70,000 美元</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-02-25/bitcoin-jumps-above-66-000-ahead-of-trump-s-address-to-congress</link><description>比特币逼近 70,000 美元水平，结束了三个交易日的连跌，因股市小幅上涨，且英伟达公司的盈利报告改善了更广泛的风险情绪。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/i3cLAyNI9ELY/v0/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 25 Feb 2026 02:19:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-02-25/bitcoin-jumps-above-66-000-ahead-of-trump-s-address-to-congress</guid></item><item><title>业绩达到最高预期后，Circle 股价创 IPO 以来最大涨幅</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-02-25/circle-s-shares-surge-after-profit-revenue-top-estimates</link><description>Circle Internet Group Inc. 表示，在第四季度数字资产低迷期间，对其稳定币的强劲需求提振了利润和收入，该公司股价上涨 35%，这是自去年高调公开亮相以来的最大涨幅。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/ia2nTk3DZthA/v0/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 25 Feb 2026 11:50:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-02-25/circle-s-shares-surge-after-profit-revenue-top-estimates</guid></item><item><title>比特币暴跌加剧了矿工之间的股市分裂</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/newsletters/2026-02-24/bitcoin-tumble-widens-stock-market-schism-among-miners</link><description>David Pan 撰写了快速发展的人工智能行业如何让股市投资者在比特币矿商中挑选赢家和输家的文章。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iMSyCna2RZAY/v1/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 24 Feb 2026 22:00:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/newsletters/2026-02-24/bitcoin-tumble-widens-stock-market-schism-among-miners</guid></item><item><title>随着数字货币的起飞，元测试稳定币支付</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-02-24/meta-testing-stablecoin-payments-as-digital-currencies-take-off</link><description>Meta Platforms Inc. 正在探索将稳定币支付集成到其应用程序中的方法，拥抱在线商务中越来越多使用的快速增长的数字货币形式。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/idnZFWFXbKsE/v1/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 24 Feb 2026 21:05:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-02-24/meta-testing-stablecoin-payments-as-digital-currencies-take-off</guid></item><item><title>随着买家的罢工，比特币的盈亏平衡陷阱正在扼杀每一次反弹</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-02-24/bitcoin-break-even-trap-is-killing-every-rally-as-buyers-strike</link><description>从加密货币顽固分子到首次 ETF 买家，通常现在会购买比特币的人都不敢这么做。数据解释了原因。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iUsowZmN6qHk/v3/1200x-1.png" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 24 Feb 2026 16:54:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-02-24/bitcoin-break-even-trap-is-killing-every-rally-as-buyers-strike</guid></item></channel></rss>